FIGS. 8A and 8B respectively illustrate the cell array and peripheral circuit portions of a semiconductor memory device having a second conductive layer formed in accordance with a first embodiment of the present invention;


FIGS. 9A and 9B respectively illustrate mask works used to form the cell array and peripheral circuit portions of a semiconductor memory device in accordance with the process steps illustrated in FIGS. 6A-8B;


